  <note type="content" displayLabel="Note">A digital version of the transcript (pdf) exists for duplication purposes; A digital version of the audio recording (mp3) exists for duplication purposes and public access in the Special Collections Reading Room; Interview conducted by David Culbert and John Hilbert.</note>
  <note type="biographical/historical" displayLabel="Biographical Note">President of the ABC News Department from 1963 to 1974 and ABC Corporate Vice President from 1974-1978.</note>
